Document: LabelSettings
Path: godot/classes/class_labelsettings.rst
Summary: This section details the properties available in LabelSettings for configuring text appearance, including font, color, size, spacing, outlines, and shadows.

*   font (Font): Font used for the text.
*   font_color (Color): Color of the text. Default: Color(1, 1, 1, 1).
*   font_size (int): Size of the text. Default: 16.
*   line_spacing (float): Additional vertical spacing between lines (in pixels), spacing is added to line descent. This value can be negative. Default: 3.0.
*   outline_color (Color): The color of the outline. Default: Color(1, 1, 1, 1).
*   outline_size (int): Text outline size. Default: 0.
*   paragraph_spacing (float): Vertical space between paragraphs. Added on top of line_spacing. Default: 0.0.
*   shadow_color (Color): Color of the shadow effect. If alpha is 0, no shadow will be drawn. Default: Color(0, 0, 0, 0).
*   shadow_offset (Vector2): Offset of the shadow effect, in pixels. Default: Vector2(1, 1).
*   shadow_size (int): Size of the shadow effect. Default: 1.
*   stacked_outline_count (int): The number of stacked outlines. Default: 0.
*   stacked_outline_{index}/color (Color): The color of the outline at index. Note: index is a value in the 0 .. stacked_outline_count - 1 range. Default: Color(0, 0, 0, 1).
*   stacked_outline_{index}/size (int): The size of the outline at index. Note: index is a value in the 0 .. stacked_outline_count - 1 range. Default: 0.
*   stacked_shadow_count (int): The number of stacked shadows. Default: 0.
*   stacked_shadow_{index}/color (Color): The color of the shadow at index. Note: index is a value in the 0 .. stacked_shadow_count - 1 range. Default: Color(0, 0, 0, 1).
*   stacked_shadow_{index}/offset (Vector2): The offset of the shadow at index. Note: index is a value in the 0 .. stacked_shadow_count - 1 range. Default: Vector2i(1, 1).
*   stacked_shadow_{index}/outline_size (int): The size of the shadow outline at index. Note: index is a value in the 0 .. stacked_shadow_count - 1 range. Default: 0.
---CHUNK---
Document: LabelSettings
Path: godot/classes/class_labelsettings.rst
Summary: This section details methods for managing stacked outlines and shadows within LabelSettings, including adding, removing, moving, and setting their properties.

Method: add_stacked_outline(index: int = -1) → void
Adds a new stacked outline to the label at the given `index`. If `index` is `-1`, the new stacked outline will be added at the end of the list.

Method: add_stacked_shadow(index: int = -1) → void
Adds a new stacked shadow to the label at the given `index`. If `index` is `-1`, the new stacked shadow will be added at the end of the list.

Method: get_stacked_outline_color(index: int) → Color
Returns the color of the stacked outline at `index`.

Method: get_stacked_outline_size(index: int) → int
Returns the size of the stacked outline at `index`.

Method: get_stacked_shadow_color(index: int) → Color
Returns the color of the stacked shadow at `index`.

Method: get_stacked_shadow_offset(index: int) → Vector2
Returns the offset of the stacked shadow at `index`.

Method: get_stacked_shadow_outline_size(index: int) → int
Returns the outline size of the stacked shadow at `index`.

Method: move_stacked_outline(from_index: int, to_position: int) → void
Moves the stacked outline at index `from_index` to the given position `to_position` in the array.

Method: move_stacked_shadow(from_index: int, to_position: int) → void
Moves the stacked shadow at index `from_index` to the given position `to_position` in the array.

Method: remove_stacked_outline(index: int) → void
Removes the stacked outline at index `index`.

Method: remove_stacked_shadow(index: int) → void
Removes the stacked shadow at index `index`.

Method: set_stacked_outline_color(index: int, color: Color) → void
Sets the color of the stacked outline identified by the given `index` to `color`.

Method: set_stacked_outline_size(index: int, size: int) → void
Sets the size of the stacked outline identified by the given `index` to `size`.

Method: set_stacked_shadow_color(index: int, color: Color) → void
Sets the color of the stacked shadow identified by the given `index` to `color`.

Method: set_stacked_shadow_offset(index: int, offset: Vector2) → void
Sets the offset of the stacked shadow identified by the given `index` to `offset`.

Method: set_stacked_shadow_outline_size(index: int, size: int) → void
Sets the outline size of the stacked shadow identified by the given `index` to `size`.